Question 1 : Convert Hexa to Binary directly

1) 12A4 --> 0001 0010 1010 0100

2) 1C35 --> 0001 1100 0011 0101

3) 100 --> 0001 0000 0000

4) 115C --> 0001 0001 0101 1100

-------------------------------------------
Question 2 : Convert Binary to Hexa directly

1) 0001 0010 1010 0100 --> 12A4

2) 0001 1100 0011 0101 --> 1C35

3) 0001 0000 0000 --> 100

4) 0001 0001 0101 1100 --> 115C
